plot: As Ryan's condition worsens, she questions Batwoman's "no killing" code when she realizes the opportunity to avenge her mother is slipping away. Tatiana fills in the gaps for Alice about her time on Coryana and her history with Ocean,

Alice finds out from a captive Tatiana why she has no memories of Ocean. Meanwhile, Ryan fights the Kryptonite poisoning to find Alice and killer in revenge for Alice killing Ryan's mother, Cora. Jacob and Sophie look for the map leading the way to Coryana, and find one of Catherine's secret projects.—Gislef
